Perfect! I now have a comprehensive understanding of the Brain project. Let me compile a complete report.

## Comprehensive Brain Project Exploration Report

### 1. GRAPH VIEW UI IMPLEMENTATION

**Main Components:**

1. **KnowledgeGraph.tsx** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/client/components/graph/KnowledgeGraph.tsx`
   - Uses **Reagraph** library (`from "reagraph"`) for force-directed 2D graph visualization
   - Renders nodes and edges with dynamic sizing based on connection count
   - Supports three query modes:
     - Focused view: centered on a single entity with configurable depth (1-3)
     - Project view: shows all entities within a project
     - Workspace overview: full workspace graph
   - Fetches from `/api/graph/{workspaceId}?center=...&depth=...` or `?project=...`
   - Selection state managed via `selectedId` prop with node click handlers

2. **GraphToolbar.tsx** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/client/components/graph/GraphToolbar.tsx`
   - Project selector dropdown
   - View mode toggle: "Project view" vs "Focused view"
   - Depth range slider (1-3) for focused view
   - Fit to view button via `graphRef.current?.fitNodesInView()`

3. **EntityDetailPanel.tsx** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/client/components/graph/EntityDetailPanel.tsx`
   - Right-side drawer showing entity details when selected
   - Displays: name, status, category, priority, confidence, created date, owner
   - Shows relationships (incoming/outgoing edges)
   - Shows provenance (source messages, documents, git commits)
   - Action buttons: confirm, override, complete, set priority, accept suggestions
   - Supports converting entities (suggestion → task/feature/decision/project)

4. **graph-theme.ts** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/client/components/graph/graph-theme.ts`
   - Color mapping for entity types (uses CSS variables):
     - Projects: blue (#3b82f6)
     - Features: teal (#14b8a6)
     - Tasks: green (#22c55e)
     - Decisions: yellow (#eab308)
     - Questions: purple (#a855f7)
     - Observations: red (#ef4444)
     - Suggestions: cyan (#06b6d4)
     - People/Identity: orange (#f97316)
   - Edge styling: different dash patterns and opacity for relationship types
     - `depends_on`: dashed, 0.8 opacity
     - `conflicts_with`: solid red, 0.9 opacity
     - `belongs_to`, `has_feature`, `has_task`: solid blue, 0.3 opacity

5. **graph-page.tsx** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/client/routes/graph-page.tsx`
   - Main page component layout
   - Integrates: KnowledgeGraph + GraphToolbar + EntityDetailPanel
   - State management via Zustand `useViewState` hook
   - Uses localStorage for active workspace persistence

**Graph API Route:**

**graph-route.ts** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/server/graph/graph-route.ts`
- Handler: `POST /api/graph/{workspaceId}`
- Query parameters:
  - `?project={projectId}` - Project view
  - `?center={entityId}&depth={1-3}` - Focused view
  - No params - Workspace overview
- Calls three query functions:
  - `getProjectGraphView()` - entities and edges for a project
  - `getFocusedGraphView()` - entity + N-hop neighbors
  - `getWorkspaceGraphOverview()` - all entities in workspace
- Transforms raw graph data via `transformToReagraph()` to Reagraph format

**Graph Query & Transform:**

**queries.ts** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/server/graph/queries.ts`
- Types: `GraphEntityTable`, `GraphViewRawEntity`, `GraphViewRawEdge`, `GraphViewRawResult`
- Entity tables included: workspace, project, person, identity, feature, task, decision, question, observation, suggestion
- Helper: `parseRecordIdString()` - parses `table:id` format with allowlist validation

**transform.ts** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/server/graph/transform.ts`
- `transformToReagraph(raw: GraphViewRawResult): GraphResponse`
- Converts raw entities/edges to Reagraph format
- Calculates connection counts with kind-based boost (projects +20, features +10, people +8)
- Maps edge kinds to title-cased labels

**Shared Contracts:**

**contracts.ts** - `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/quebec/app/src/shared/contracts.ts`
- `EntityKind`: "workspace" | "project" | "person" | "identity" | "feature" | "task" | "decision" | "question" | "observation" | "suggestion" | "message" | "agent_session" | "intent"
- `ReagraphNode`: `{ id, label, fill, data: { kind, connectionCount, status? } }`
- `ReagraphEdge`: `{ id, source, target, label, data: { type, confidence } }`
- `GraphResponse`: `{ nodes: ReagraphNode[], edges: ReagraphEdge[] }`

